# FILE: halabFreelance/topTalentLeaderboard/topTalentLeaderboard.desc
# ROLE: Hall of Fame & Competitive Ranking
# ROUTE: /freelance/leaderboard
# ACCOUNT: All can view — logged-in freelancers see their personal rank
# THEME: Dark · gold/silver/bronze podium · power list table

## 1. PODIUM (Top 3 Elite)
- LAYOUT: 3-col "victory stand" layout
- RANK 1 (CENTER): largest card · gold border (border-[#F59E0B]/60) · [👑 النخبة] badge
- RANK 2 (RIGHT): silver border (border-[#94A3B8]/40)
- RANK 3 (LEFT): bronze border (border-[#CD7C3A]/40)
- EACH CARD: large avatar + name + freelancer type badge + total jobs + rating score
- ACTION: [👤 عرض الملف] → /freelance/profile/:id

## 2. DYNAMIC FILTER BAR
- CATEGORY FILTER: 💻 برمجة · 🏗️ هندسة · 🎨 تصميم · ✍️ كتابة ...
- FREELANCER TYPE: [🎓 طلابي] [💼 خارجي] [الكل]
- SORT: الأعلى ربحاً · الأسرع استجابةً · الأعلى تقييماً
- TIMELINE: [📅 هذا الشهر] [🏆 كل الأوقات]

## 3. POWER LIST (Rank 4–100)
- STYLE: vertical list · alternating bg-[#0F1828]/bg-[#162032] rows
- COLUMNS:
  - RANK: #4, #5 ... monospace bold
  - USER: avatar + name + freelancer type badge
  - DISCIPLINE: "هندسة وعمارة"
  - POWER METER: horizontal bar (0–100%) — indigo fill
  - SUCCESS RATE: "98% إتمام"
- HOVER: row bg shifts to bg-[#6366F1]/10

## 4. YOUR RANK (Sticky Bottom — Logged-in Freelancers Only)
- Shown when accountType === 'student' && isFreelancer || businessType === 'freelancer'
- DISPLAY: "ترتيبك الحالي: #156 — تحتاج 4 تقييمات إضافية لدخول أفضل 100"
- CTA: [📈 تحسين نقاطي] → tips on how to rank higher

## 5. HALL OF FAME REWARDS (Sidebar Card)
- Benefits of Top 100:
  - عمولة أقل بنسبة 50%
  - [💎 VIP] badge on all service listings
  - Priority placement in freelance catalog
